text: Victory at Entebbe is a 1976 American television drama movie directed by Marvin J. Chomsky. It stars Julius Harris, Anthony Hopkins, Burt Lancaster, Elizabeth Taylor, Linda Blair, Richard Dreyfuss, Helmut Berger, Kirk Douglas and Jessica Walter. It was distributed by David L. Wolper Productions. ==Other websites== * * Category:1976 drama movies Category:Television movies Category:American drama movies Category:Movies set in Uganda Category:Movies directed by Marvin J.
